-- 
Roche Drug Wins U.K. Backing for Advanced Follicular Lymphoma

-- B y   K r i s t e n   H a l l a m
-- 
2011-09-04T23:01:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-04/roche-drug-wins-u-k-backing-for-advanced-follicular-lymphoma.html
Roche Holding AG (ROG) ’s MabThera drug won
the backing of the U.K.’s National Institute for Health and
Clinical Excellence in draft guidelines that would expand the
number of chemotherapy regimens recommended for use with
MabThera in treating advanced follicular lymphoma, according to
an e-mailed statement from the institute.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kristen Hallam in London at 
 khallam@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
